Materials Needed for Camera
1. Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W with Soldered 40-Pin Header
2. Raspberry Pi High Quality Camera
3. Raspberry Pi Standard-Mini Camera Cable
4. 6mm 3MP Wide Angle Lens for Raspberry Pi HQ Camera - 3MP
5. Witty Pi 4 Mini
6. SanDisk 32 GB MicroSD Card
7. Micro USB to USB A OTG Adapter 
8. Samsung FIT Plus 256 GB Flash Drive

Supplementary Hardware
1. Monitor with HDMI input
2. Mini HDMI to HDMI Cable
3. Keyboard
4. Mouse
5. Micro USB to USB OTG Hub
6. Micro USB Power Cable for Raspberry Pi Zero
7. USB-C Power Cable for Witty Pi 4 Mini
8. SanDisk microSD adapter

Steps to Configure Hardware
1. Connect camera via cable to Raspberry Pi
2. Connect Witty Pi to Raspberry Pi
